<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 01:21:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Deep Research Max：自主研究代理的一步变革</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/deep-research-max-a-step-change-for-autonomous-research-agents</link><description>隆重推出 Deep Research 和 Deep Research Max，这是 Google 的下一代自主研究代理。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/deep-research-max-a-step-change-for-autonomous-research-agents2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 01:21:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/deep-research-max-a-step-change-for-autonomous-research-agents</guid></item><item><title>博格立方体的不可能工程</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-impossible-engineering-of-the-borg-cube</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 01:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-impossible-engineering-of-the-borg-cube</guid></item><item><title>东映公司推出发行品牌 Toei Games</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/toei-company-launches-publishing-label-toei-games</link><description>日本娱乐公司东映 (Toei) 成立了内部出版品牌东映游戏 (Toei Games)。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/toei-company-launches-publishing-label-toei-games.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/toei-company-launches-publishing-label-toei-games</guid></item><item><title>智能层级：人工智能的未来属于个体创造者</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/intelligence-hierarchy-the-future-of-artificial-intelligence-belongs-to-the-individual-creators</link><description>当人工智能热潮开始时，它并不是一个开放、互联的乌托邦。从第一天起，它就建立在筒仓中。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/intelligence-hierarchy-the-future-of-artificial-intelligence-belongs-to-the-individual-creators.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/intelligence-hierarchy-the-future-of-artificial-intelligence-belongs-to-the-individual-creators</guid></item><item><title>Nvidia 的 Jensen Huang 警告称，运行在华为芯片上的 DeepSeek 对美国来说将是“可怕的结果”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nvidias-jensen-huang-warns-deepseek-running-on-huawei-chips-would-be-horrible-outcome-for-america</link><description>英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋表示，DeepSeek 为华为 Ascend 芯片而不是美国硬件优化人工智能模型将“对美国来说是一个可怕的结果”。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nvidias-jensen-huang-warns-deepseek-running-on-huawei-chips-would-be-horrible-outcome-for-america.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nvidias-jensen-huang-warns-deepseek-running-on-huawei-chips-would-be-horrible-outcome-for-america</guid></item><item><title>异常的多细胞干扰素信号传导是 Adar1 突变驱动的 Aicardi-Goutières 综合征样脑病的基础</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/aberrant-multicellular-interferon-signaling-underlies-adar1-mutation-driven-aicardi-goutieres-syndrome-like-encephalopathy</link><description>尤等人。证明 Z-RNA 结合缺陷的 ADAR1 会触发多细胞 I 型干扰素的异常产生，尤其是星形胶质细胞的干扰素产生，并在小鼠中诱导明显的室周脑病。阻断 I 型干扰素信号传导可完全挽救病理，表明 I 型干扰素的心室积聚是脑室周围脑病的主要驱动因素。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/aberrant-multicellular-interferon-signaling-underlies-adar1-mutation-driven-aicardi-goutieres-syndrome-like-encephalopathy2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/aberrant-multicellular-interferon-signaling-underlies-adar1-mutation-driven-aicardi-goutieres-syndrome-like-encephalopathy</guid></item><item><title>回避学习中的脑-脂肪体轴</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/brain-fat-body-axis-in-avoidance-learning</link><description>目前尚不清楚免疫系统发现病原体如何导致行为改变。 “由于这种习得性食物回避现象在所有物种中都存在，因此我们在模式生物——果蝇——果蝇中研究了这个问题，”资深作者解释道。 “在这个模型中，我们可以阐明大脑和身体如何相互作用以触发对生存至关重要的回避反应。”&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/brain-fat-body-axis-in-avoidance-learning2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/brain-fat-body-axis-in-avoidance-learning</guid></item><item><title>生成式人工智能改进了无线视觉系统，可以穿透障碍物</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/generative-ai-improves-a-wireless-vision-system-that-sees-through-obstructions</link><description>Wave-Former 是一种新系统，可以完成隐藏 3D 物体的形状或使用反射的无线信号重建整个内部房间的场景。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/generative-ai-improves-a-wireless-vision-system-that-sees-through-obstructions3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/generative-ai-improves-a-wireless-vision-system-that-sees-through-obstructions</guid></item><item><title>SwRI 领导的研究表明太阳的磁引擎更为复杂</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/swri-led-research-indicates-a-more-complex-suns-magnetic-engine</link><description>仔细观察发现质子和重离子超出了预期。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/swri-led-research-indicates-a-more-complex-suns-magnetic-engine.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 11:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/swri-led-research-indicates-a-more-complex-suns-magnetic-engine</guid></item><item><title>视网膜血管指纹预测中风事件：英国生物银行队列研究的结果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/retinal-vascular-fingerprints-predict-incident-stroke-findings-from-the-uk-biobank-cohort-study</link><description>目的 研究一组全面的视网膜血管参数与卒中事件之间的关联，以揭示新的关联并探索其对卒中风险的预测能力。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/retinal-vascular-fingerprints-predict-incident-stroke-findings-from-the-uk-biobank-cohort-study2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 11:43:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/retinal-vascular-fingerprints-predict-incident-stroke-findings-from-the-uk-biobank-cohort-study</guid></item></channel></rss>